<BaseLayout title="Contact Us - cameraupick" description="Get in touch with cameraupick. Questions about our reviews, partnership inquiries, or feedback.">
<main id="main" class="container">
    <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-grid">
                <div>
                    <h1>Contact Us</h1>
                    <p class="hero-sub">Have questions, feedback, or partnership inquiries? We'd love to hear from you.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="section">
            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
            <p>We read every message and respond to legitimate inquiries within 2-3 business days. Please note: we do
                not accept paid placements, sponsored reviews, or manufacturer pressure of any kind.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));">
                <article class="card card-plain">
                    <h3>üìß General Inquiries</h3>
                    <p>Questions about our reviews, methodology, or suggestions for future content.</p>
                    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:cameraupick@gmail.com"
                            style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none;">cameraupick@gmail.com</a></p>
                </article>

                <article class="card card-plain">
                    <h3>ü§ù Partnerships</h3>
                    <p>Press releases, partnership opportunities, or brand inquiries (no paid placements).</p>
                    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:cameraupick@gmail.com"
                            style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none;">cameraupick@gmail.com</a></p>
                </article>

                <article class="card card-plain">
                    <h3>üêõ Technical Issues</h3>
                    <p>Found a broken link, typo, or technical bug on the site?</p>
                    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:cameraupick@gmail.com"
                            style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none;">cameraupick@gmail.com</a></p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-container">
                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>Do you accept review units from manufacturers?</summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>No. We purchase or rent all cameras ourselves to maintain complete independence. This ensures
                            our reviews are unbiased and honest.</p>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>Can I sponsor a review or get my product featured?</summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>No. We do not accept paid placements, sponsored content, or any form of compensation that
                            would influence our editorial decisions. Our top picks are based solely on merit.</p>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>How do you make money?</summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We use affiliate links (primarily Amazon Associates). When you purchase through our links, we
                            earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This keeps the site ad-free while
                            maintaining editorial independence.</p>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>Can you review a specific camera?</summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We appreciate suggestions! Email us at cameraupick@gmail.com with your request. We prioritize
                            cameras based on reader interest and availability, but we can't guarantee coverage of every
                            request.</p>
                    </div>
                </details>

                <details class="faq-item">
                    <summary>Do you offer consulting or custom recommendations?</summary>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We don't offer one-on-one consulting, but our buying guides are designed to answer most
                            questions. If you need specific advice, email us‚Äîwe often respond with personalized
                            recommendations when time permits.</p>
                    </div>
                </details>
            </div>
        </section>

